#: ../../source/example_gallery/dataset.rst:54 e51d464bcba3485c8f8f1175f05a22de
msgid ""
"The 2D RHS shape ``[n_inner, batch]`` is auto-routed to a SuperLU direct "
"solve: one factorization, ``batch`` back-substitutions. A ``--mode "
"bench`` benchmark sweeps batch sizes from 1 to 1024 and reports per-"
"problem timing on CPU and GPU; the per-problem cost drops sharply with "
"batch size as the factorization overhead is amortized."
msgstr ""

